The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and algorithms (cs.DS), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and economic theory (cs.EC). The use of posted price mechanisms and the focus on revenue optimization suggest a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
